title: I have played so many games by now
body: Yet somehow there are still a handful of champs I have never played once in my life, anyone else like this or is it just me?

replies.body: I have played since season 1. No honor ribbon. Does anyone else feel this way?

Never played champs like kat, annie, jinx, zed, gnar, reksai, warwick, mus%%%%


edit highkek you cant say must.ard
I have a grand total of two champs I have never played. {{champion:131}}  and {{champion:106}}

haha that was my first goal, there still are ones that ive only played a few times like galio, heimer, poppy, naut, taric, just something so fun about playing something ive never played before
